  <original-body>This patch adds special AssociationReflection methods for creating association objects, and modifies the code base to use those methods instead of creating association objects directly. This allows plugins to hook into association object creation behavior.

For example,

  @reflection.klass.new(...)

now becomes

  @reflection.build_association(...)

Is this patch simple enough to make it into 2.2?</original-body>
